        <mxCell id="Ae09-KmcBkR8viZgckkO-56" value="unapproved_deposits_handler.py&lt;br&gt;Explanation&amp;nbsp;:&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;adds unapproved deposits, removes approved deposits that created before, and looks for unapproved deposits that are matching to unmatched withdrawals and removes these deposits (deposits cancellations) and removes deposits that have been cancelled on the CRM.&lt;br&gt;Uses the rest of the unmatched deposits to check if a client transferred between accounts.&lt;br&gt;Creates the remaining unmatched deposits and unmatched withdrawals on seperate files&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=ext;margin=3;double=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
